Module jakarta.resource
Package jakarta.resource.cci

Interface IndexedRecord<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, List<E>, Record, Serializable
    public interface IndexedRecord<E>
extends Record, List<E>, Serializable
    IndexedRecord represents an ordered collection of record elements based on the java.util.List interface. This interface allows a client to access elements by their integer index (position in the list) and search for elements in the List.
    Since:
    0.8
    Author:
    Rahul Sharma
